Installation
------------

To install using the GNU Build System method, just open a terminal and
type the following commands:

	username@host: dir $ git clone https://github.com/ddwek/textscreen_ruler.git ./ruler
	username@host: dir $ cd ruler
	username@host: nullify $ ./configure --prefix=/usr/local
	username@host: nullify $ make
	[ become superuser if needed ]
	username@host: nullify $ make install
